        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Make recommended the default skill ranking",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- makes `recommended` the canonical public skill sort for the web browse and home feeds\n- keeps old `default` sort input as a compatibility alias\n- adds `sort=recommended` support to `/api/v1/skills` while preserving the v1 no-sort `updated` default\n- ranks recommended results by stars, all-time installs, downloads, then updated time\n- updates search popularity scoring so downloads are only a fallback signal\n- adds digest index/backfill support, docs, and regression tests for ranking and sort-state behavior\n\n## Tests\n\nPassed on the rebased head:\n\n- `git diff --check`\n- `bun run format:check`\n- `bun run lint`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bun run test -- src/__tests__/skills-index.test.tsx src/__tests__/skills-route-default-sort.test.ts src/__tests__/home-route.test.tsx convex/skills.listPublicPageV4.test.ts convex/skills.publicListCursor.test.ts convex/search.test.ts convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts convex/lib/skillSearchDigest.test.ts`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bun run test -- convex/maintenance.test.ts convex/skills.ownership.test.ts convex/skills.publicListCursor.test.ts`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bun run test -- convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts convex/skills.listPublicPageV4.test.ts src/__tests__/skills-index.test.tsx src/__tests__/home-route.test.tsx`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/schema/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/clawhub/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bun run --cwd packages/clawhub-mod typecheck`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bun run build`\n\nAttempted but blocked by an existing dependency issue:\n\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bun run test` passed 230/232 test files and 2567/2567 tests, then failed two `scripts/public-corpus/*` suites because `scripts/public-corpus/dummyOwners.ts` imports missing `@faker-js/faker`.\n- `bunx tsc --noEmit` fails for the same missing `@faker-js/faker` import in `scripts/public-corpus/dummyOwners.ts`.\n\n## Prod-data preview\n\n- Read `skillSearchDigest` from prod deployment `wry-manatee-359` using read-only CLI access.\n- Built a local snapshot preview for the actual `/skills` page with the PR ranking formula.\n- Verified `/skills?prodSnapshot=1` in Playwright; top rows were:\n  1. `@pskoett/Self-Improving Agent`\n  2. `@ivangdavila/Self-Improving + Proactive Agent`\n  3. `@spclaudehome/Skill Vetter`\n  4. `@steipete/Gog`\n  5. `@halthelobster/Proactive Agent`\n\n## Notes\n\n- Convex prod export/import for a full cloned dev deployment is blocked by missing backup/export permission (`CreateBackups`).\n- `convex logs --failure` is not supported by the installed Convex CLI.\n- Local UI screenshots were captured for `/skills` mobile and desktop after confirming Recommended defaults and search switches to Relevance.\n",
